{"tid":110710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過馬路疑冇睇燈 66歲路人遭小巴撞倒昏迷","createTime":"2017-02-07T01:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T17:04:55.000Z","uid":122,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36961ea86435cd92ff11950b6f05f923c90495e6","tid":110710,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T01:36:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>過馬路疑冇睇燈 路人遭小巴撞倒昏迷</strong><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣禮頓道36號對開，早上6時許，一名66歲姓黃男子，在燈位橫過馬路時遭一輛專線小巴撞倒，頭部重傷昏迷地上滿地鮮血。隨後駛至的士亦輾過路面鮮血，車胎沾有血迹。途人上前協助傷者，並要的士司機留在現場，等待警員調查。傷者稍後由救護員送院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n61歲姓黃小巴司機表示，當時車上滿載乘客，他沿綠燈行車，看不到有人過馬路，及至撞到人馬上停下，車上乘客亦大叫撞倒人，小巴左邊車頭損毀。警方初步調查後，以涉嫌不小心駕駛將他拘捕帶署。<br />\n<br />\n至於62歲姓孫的士司機聲言沒有再撞到該名傷者，駛至時已發生意外，只是車胎沾染到血迹。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170207/56271349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170207%2F56271349&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUahv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d5bc2979\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170207%2F56271349&h=65c341b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170207/56271349</a>"},{"pid":"4c19fd259600f166927595a7995fa23e347b8899","tid":110710,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T01:37:24.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"618802f2624a91e8819c06c15bd4c6b1b240813a","tid":110710,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T01:39:41.000Z","msg":"噓 傻仔先等綠燈"},{"pid":"62ac9476c5a47cf36d4a35a21e416ba75db71b15","tid":110710,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T01:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>噓 傻仔先等綠燈</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4299ee773fa52fa2c7ca36a24e1f19c78864aa4","tid":110710,"uid":69403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T01:57:57.000Z","msg":"都唔知班野個腦裝緊乜"},{"pi